  "31fbdfbb-0bcf-4747-a68c-ed0767316919"],
 " \[LongDash] n gamma matrices satisfying the Clifford relation for an \
arbitrary real symmetric metric in any dimension"
}], "GuideText",
 CellID->537179840,ExpressionUUID->"22853851-f777-47fd-b633-945d7798e646"],

Cell[TextData[{
