], "InlineGuideFunction",ExpressionUUID->
  "9973ea17-7873-4148-a80d-1cbaf35b7cb4"],
 " \[LongDash] flat Euclidean gamma matrices in the Brauer\[Dash]Weyl (Pauli\
\[Dash]Kronecker) representation"
}], "GuideText",
 CellID->1085639662,ExpressionUUID->"67eb4609-a6fc-41db-ae11-75ea5b1c7ee7"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

