  "InlineGuideFunction",ExpressionUUID->
  "498f1446-15ff-444d-84d9-bf8d31a5ba10"],
 " \[LongDash] diagonal flat metric of signature (p, q)"
}], "GuideText",
 CellID->1695579183,ExpressionUUID->"94857958-5ed1-4327-b3f9-72fa9b6e63b4"],

Cell[TextData[{
