  ButtonBox["RandomCurvedMetric",
   BaseStyle->"Link",
   ButtonData->
    "paclet:WolframQuantumComputation/DiracMatrix/ref/RandomCurvedMetric"]], 
  "InlineGuideFunction",ExpressionUUID->
  "2d1b1363-5910-4aca-a8e6-0ead0546fcbe"],
 " \[LongDash] random real symmetric non-diagonal metric of given signature, \
with a controllable condition number"
}], "GuideText",
 CellID->516547027,ExpressionUUID->"d0aa8390-7fa5-458d-962d-a6f9f021dd78"],

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData[
