  "e72f4ed8-3566-4013-a6a4-0c2fc61c92ab"],
 " \[LongDash] transform gamma matrices from the Brauer\[Dash]Weyl basis to \
the Weyl (chiral) basis"
}], "GuideText",
 CellID->1094046455,ExpressionUUID->"6f24d907-b40b-45a8-984a-1b7cb26daddc"]
}, Open  ]],

